Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring training was awesome, but\NI can't wait to see my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch up on some\NDaring Do with Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,help Applejack make\Nmy favorite cider,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and have a sleepover\Nwith Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it, you have\Na fun week planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile I'm stuck here running\Ntrials week at the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you love yelling and\Nblowing your whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you gals later!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, the map!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Twilight! So\Nwhere am I going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Mountains?\NVanhoover? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the good news is we\Nboth got called by the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome! Does that\Nmean there's bad news?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Well, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, I was just there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\NBy YayPonies\NMuffins Trails\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right newbies,\Nwelcome to trials week
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Wonderbolt Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be judged on your\Nspeed, strength, agility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and technique, culminating\Nin a final evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be hard? Yes.\NWill you cry? Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you fly so much\Nyour wings fall off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That has only happened once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just exaggerating\Nto make a point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, wings can't\Nreally fall off, can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you've got what it\Ntakes to be an elite flyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.46,0:02:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me tell\Nyou, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when she\Nsaid that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[excited hero-worship chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think Rainbow\NDash is the pony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,whose wings fell\Noff, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit yer whisperin' and give me\Nfive hundred laps! Go go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I just wanted you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are my favorite\Nponies in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't that sweet. Now\Nget going on those laps!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Princess\NTwilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nback so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Official Friendship business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed anypony having\Na hard time with their friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. But it's\Nnot my job to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,about their relationships. I'm\Nhere to make them elite fliers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Adorable. They're so full\Nof hope and competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Their technique could\Nuse some work, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'd appreciate\Nany notes from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. I wouldn't want to\Nmess with their confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But they'll never get better if\Nthey don't know what to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sloppy wing placement.\NCrooked lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have to drill\Nthem on basic technique
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the classroom portion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Classroom portion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's everypony's least\Nfavorite part of trial week,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but it has to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We can?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Between your flying skills\Nand my teaching expertise,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they could learn a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, once they get to know us,\Nthey'll be more comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,coming to us with their\Nfriendship problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Count us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have your work\Ncut out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness I had time\Nto whip up a few charts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,on flight patterns\Nand wing symmetry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fresh in my mind from\Nwhen I learned to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe for you. I\Npractically fell asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,when I went through\Nthis. Tell ya what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the\Nteaching stuff to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll just make\Nsure they stay awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure their thirst\Nfor knowledge will keep them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,bright-eyed and bushy tailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[laugh] Good\None, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, newbies!\NClass is in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, students!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Twilight Sparkle and\Nthis is Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can call us T-Sparks\Nand the Dashinator!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're here to go over\Nbasic flying technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uggggggh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Me. I mean, we're here because\Nwe're amazingly awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,crazy good flyers. We're\Nwaaaaay past basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky Stinger. You've\Nnever heard of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He set the record\Nfor the fastest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,vertical acceleration rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,500 feet in two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can talk personal\Nrecords after class, Ms--?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Vapor Trail. She's my wingpony.\NI never fly without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll have to\Nin the solo trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There are solo trials?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. It's a part of\Nyour final evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ace that test with our\Nwings tied behind our flanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My picture will go\Nright up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...next to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mighty big claim\Nconsidering everypony here is an
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"amazingly awesome\Ncrazy good flyer."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!\NLet's get back on track.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who can tell me\Nthe best wing angle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to achieve minimal\Nair resistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, newbies!\NClass is in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there were a\Nfew hiccups,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but overall that\Nwent pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Nopony fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm not\Na student!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Or Twilight?\NProbably Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, both. About\Nthe solo test,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually kinda\Nworried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw. That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have moments\Nwhere we doubt ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No. I have absolutely\Nzero doubts about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a strong flyer--like\Nreally, really, really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But this isn't about me.\NI'm worried for Vapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well... that is\Nvery... kind? Of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell you what. It's almost\Ntime for freestyle training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you grab her and\Nshow us what you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Prepare to be\Nimpressed. By me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, Vapor\Nstill needs work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he may be full of\Nhimself but I have to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky's an excellent flyer. He\Nmust've shot up 200 feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.02,0:07:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But did you see Vapor Trail?\NHer wing was under his.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she gave him a boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I didn't\Neven notice Vapor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too busy\Nwatching Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Vapor just created a gust of\Nwind that caught Sky's wing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,at a 45 degree angle, propelling\Nhim into a flipping loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony paid\Nattention in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky obviously has no\Nidea he's not actually
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"amazingly awesome".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Vapor's so busy making\Nher friend look good,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,she's not focused on\Nher own flying at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be our\Nfriendship problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's only\None thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Fix it without telling them!\NTell them the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want\Nto tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Flying\Nis like 30 percent skill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and 70 percent confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't mess with\Na flier's confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't improve if you\Ndon't think you have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Vapor's keeping a\Npretty big secret from Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and that can lead\Nto trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but if we tell\Nthem that they've been
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,holding each other back,\Nthat could be trouble too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I nailed that\Nflipping loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually surprised\Nyou're still here;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I blew\Nyou away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You were great,\NSky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Vapor Trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to\Nbuild up your endurance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,if you want a shot\Nat the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolts don't\Nget winded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel Wings! You call\Nthat cloud busting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That cloud barely\Nknew you were there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep working\Nand who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,One day you might come close\Nto being almost as good as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You were voted Stratusberg's\NMost Promising Flier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was voted\NBest Sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You do have a\Nreally great sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sky. But I don't\Nthink I can sneeze my way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,into the Academy.\NI'm pretty beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hit the showers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she's\Nnot the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you did great. You're\Na really strong flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vapor Trail, we know\Nwhat you've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been doing... great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been helping Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky doesn't need anypony's\Nhelp. He's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not without you. And it's\Ngonna be pretty obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,during the solo trials when\Nhe can't get enough air
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to do a flipping loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. I can't let\Nthat happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean--aww, sugarcubes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing\Nthis for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It started when we were kids.\NYou have to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sky grew up with a lot\Nof siblings. It was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always trying to\Nget his parents' attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, I was an only child\Nwho hated all the attention
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Vapor Trail! Where are you?\NDo you need a snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to do homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or we can just spend\Nsome time together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All day is never enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Dad! Up here! Look, look,\Nlook, look, look, look, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Dad! Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying together gave\Nus both what we wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never told Sky how\Nmuch I was helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It started with a\Nsmall boost here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,or a little gust of\Nwind there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't think my help could\Nactually hurt his chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. But now\Nyou're both in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to work\Non your tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sky needs to be able to fly\Nwithout you or he won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but he has to! Flying\Nwith the Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,has been Sky's dream\Never since he was a colt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I guess I haven't\Nthought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to be\Nwith my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have to find a\Nway to help both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with telling\NSky the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't. Sky\Nwill be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And without his confidence\Nhe won't fly as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess we'll give\NDash's method a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I love being right.\NOK. Here's what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky needs to build his strength.\NAir drills, wing lifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,all that boring,\Nmethodical stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like my\Ncup of oats.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But how will we\Nget him to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't think\Nhe needs practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just tell Sky that he\Nshould practice with Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so you won't feel so\Nself-conscious about getting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,special training from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With you? Really?\NYou'd do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. You say that like\Nit's not gonna be a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You were awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thanks! I can't\Nbelieve I was able to keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first nice thing I've\Nheard you say about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we switch now? I want to\Ndo tricks with Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't. I mean... uh\Nyou're already so good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,at the fancy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the basic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I don't\Nneed to practice at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. Maybe, Sky,\Nyou should...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already the best and\Neverypony's gonna know it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm asked to join\Nthe Academy tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But not if you\Ndon't practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be surprised if they\Nasked me to become a Wonderbolt
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,straight out of the trials!\NBoom. Dream achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,SKY YOU'RE NOT AS GOOD\NAS YOU THINK YOU ARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky. I want you to get\Nin as much as anypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're amazing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been... helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. I don't need\Nyour help. Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you do this\Nto me? Did you all know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh great. So everypony\Nbut me knows I'm a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this your plan the whole\Ntime? To embarrass me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No! Don't\Nyou know me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not since it took\Nme this long to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a terrible wingpony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I\Nwas ever your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think\Nthey're still mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're still mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault. If we\Nhad just done things your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we could've\Navoided this whole mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It hit me when I was\Nwatching Sky train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't even trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no. He's lost\Nhis confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to tell me why one\Nof my most promising students
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is flying like a balloon\Nwith a hole in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's a long story,\Nbut we'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We really messed up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sky. I thought I\Nmight find you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, apparently I\Nneed a lot of practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'm not the\Nnatural I thought I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Good pep talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't a natural\Nat friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But with some practice and\Nsome help from my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got better. And now? I'm\Nthe Princess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying I can be\Nthe Princess of Flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're really good.\NYou're lead pony material.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sweet of you, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't handle\Nall the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll never\Nbecome a Wonderbolt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're too afraid to shine.\NThat is what you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at first. I just\Nwanted to be with Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But learning to do all\Nthose fun tricks with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me realize this is\Nsomething I want for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you'd say\Nthat. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky, Vapor was never trying\Nto steal your spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought she\Nwas helping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And Vapor, you shouldn't\Nhave been so content
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to take a back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can either stay\Nmad, or help each other
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and become two of\Nthe greatest fliers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the Wonderbolt\NAcademy has ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pick the second option.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want Spitfire\Nto be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got this, Sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on a cloud\Nwhen you spin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll help you fly straight\Nwhen you come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo! Yeah! Ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, way to go! Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've both made it into\Nthe Wonderbolt Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you\Ndid, it worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,These two have a\Nlot of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? They might even\Nbe better than you, Crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OK,\Nlet's not get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.43,0:20:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I just wanted\Nyou to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are my new favorite\Nponies in all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I heard that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nwe did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You were great! Even\Nthough you can out-fly me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be my\Nwingpony anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! It's good to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me. Now\Nwe can finally catch up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,on some Daring Do; I can\Nmake cider with Applejack...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash! I've been looking\Nall over for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderbolt emergency!\NWe gotta get back to HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding\Nme! I was JUST there!
